p: Herman Tse**#{27}":[46,46],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{28}":[47,47],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{29}":[48,48],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{30}":[49,49],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{31}":[50,50],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{32}":[51,51],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{33}":[52,52],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{34}":[53,53],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{35}":[54,54],"###**Call Prep: Herman Tse**#{36}":[55,64],"#key_language: Any transformation in his eyes needs to be evidence based. However the GM's he talks to and other stakeholders are either too risk averse, or a structure / leadership change just changes things without much consideration.":[65,65],"#messy_problem: Speed to get the foundation data gathering and testing for decisions on big investments. The leaders don't want to wait that long.":[66,66],"#messy_problem: Cultural - organisations don't understand what AI is. they struggle to utilize it appropriately.":[67,67],"#messy_problem: Cyber Risk - Clients often don't understand just how vulnerable their data is. it only takes a few prompts and he can hack into an LLM and get the data.":[68,68],"#messy_problem: Media spreading anti-AI rumours which causes issues":[69,69],"#action_item: Book in more time with Anthony to stay in touch. he wants me to join Student alumni events, possibly go down to Melbourne":[70,70],"#action_item: Read Herman's papers.":[71,71],"#action_item: Research ways to automate the research and data gathering for the discovery phase of projects":[72,72]},"outlinks":[],"metadata":{"tags":["#1-2","#messy_problem","#action_item"]},"task_lines":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"16qsg4k","at":1762219683749},"key":"docs/Stakeholder Engagment/C1 - Herman Tse/C1 - Herman Tse Call Notes.md"},
